acceptOwnership().details: New owner pending to accept ownership executes this function to confirm his ownership.

disableDeposits().details: Disable deposits if they are enabled, executed only by admin. Emits DepositsDisabled event.

disableWithdrawals().details: Disable withdrawals if they are enabled, executed only by admin. Emits WithdrawalsDisabled event.

enableDeposits().details: Enable deposits if they are disabled, executed only by admin. Emits DepositsEnabled event.

enableDeposits(bool).details: Enable/Disable deposits, executed only by admin.

enableWithdrawals().details: Enable withdrawals if they are disabled, executed only by admin. Emits WithdrawalsEnabled event.

enableWithdrawals(bool).details: Enable/Disable withdrawals, executed only by admin.

setMaxWithdrawalAmount(uint256).details: Set/change maximum withdrawal amount, only admin can do it.

setMinWithdrawalAmount(uint256).details: Set/change minimum withdrawal amount, only admin can do it.

params._newOwner: New owner address acquiring ownership of contract
